parties: In the Matter of DISCIPLINE OF Dean I. ORLOFF.
casebody.head_matter:
In the Matter of DISCIPLINE OF Dean I. ORLOFF.
No. D-2953.
Supreme Court of the United States
March 20, 2017.
Dean I. Orloff, of Mt. Laurel, New Jersey, is suspended from the practice of law in this Court and a rule will issue, returnable within 40 days, requiring him to show cause why he should not be disbarred from the practice of law in this Court.
